<topic id="how-to-documentum-xdb">
  <title>Configuring a <ph keyref="xhiveDB"/> Database Connection</title>
  <body>
    <p>Follow this procedure to configure the support for a <ph keyref="xhiveDB"/> database:<ol>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-xhive-datasource.dita#configure-xhive-datasource"
            >Configure Documentum xDB <term>Data Source</term> drivers</xref>.</li>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-xhive-connection.dita#configure-xhive-connection"
            >Configure a Documentum xDB <term>Connection</term></xref>.</li>
        <li>To view your connection, go to the <xref
            href="../topics/relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"
              ><uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>
          <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view-parenthesis"/> or switch to the
            <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
          <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"><term>perspective</term></xref>.</li>
      </ol></p>
  </body>
